{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"318ae66629","title":"第六号通令","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cbb3b09808","index":0,"year":1966,"month":9,"day":9,"articleId":"318ae66629","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"红卫兵运动","id":"3be4d5766f","type":"主题"},{"name":"暴力和武斗","id":"3bff1d2fc6","type":"主题"},{"name":"群众运动重要文献","id":"4bd6d6f93a","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"89d86a8bd3","name":"《首都红卫兵纠察队》西城指挥部"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"21e5de01d9","type":"title","text":"第六号通令","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"414f52d93f","type":"paragraph","text":"要摆事实，讲道理，防止简单、粗暴的做法，严禁打人和其他形式的体罚，防止逼、供、信。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b97a422ccc","type":"paragraph","text":"──《二十三条》","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6a8a75a79a","type":"paragraph","text":"用文斗，不用武斗，这是党在无产阶级文化大革命中的一项重要政策。我们一定要坚持这个政策，贯彻执行这个政策。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5263bfde40","type":"paragraph","text":"──《人民日报》社论","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8961815cca","type":"paragraph","text":"关于文斗问题的补充说明","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"df545db6fc","type":"paragraph","text":"本部于九月三日颁布了第五号通令。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7f7be2dee0","type":"paragraph","text":"通令中说：“为了捍卫毛泽东思想，为了执行党的政策，为了按照《十六条》办事，把无产阶级文化大革命搞深、搞透、搞彻底，在今后的文化革命运动中，严禁打人，严禁体罚及变相体罚，严禁侮辱人，严禁逼供信。”","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"903622b64c","type":"paragraph","text":"由于通令中所说的不够具体，现在我们特作如下补充。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0a9963a732","type":"paragraph","text":"一、 关于文斗","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"80a508a8a1","type":"paragraph","text":"我们要坚持文斗，不用武斗，打人、体罚及变相体罚、侮辱人、逼供信、等等，都不是文斗，都不是我们所应采取的斗争方法。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0c795ee250","type":"paragraph","text":"二、关于体罚及变相体罚","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2eef845e14","type":"paragraph","text":"跪、趴、弯腰、负重、游街、长时间站立、长时间举手、长时间低头、长时间做重活，等等，都属于体罚及变相体罚，都不是我们所应采取的斗争方法。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"131a8e32b3","type":"paragraph","text":"三、关于侮辱人","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"848e68f40e","type":"paragraph","text":"“挂黑牌”，“戴高帽”，“唱嚎歌”，“剃光头”等等，都属于侮辱人，都不是我们所应采取的斗争方法。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0994efd4cd","type":"paragraph","text":"四、关于逼供信","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1d01cba75f","type":"paragraph","text":"不注重调查研究，不注重事实证据，反而片面轻信口供，迷信口供，并用武斗或威胁的方法逼人口供，逼出来了就信，这就叫逼供信。这种做法是盲目的，极易被坏人利用，这不是我们所应采取的斗争方法。","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"78251592a3","type":"paragraph","text":"五、关于劳动","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7da479bd1e","type":"paragraph","text":"应该组织参加劳动，这样便于对那些人进行改造，但一定要区别对待，一定要适量，老弱病残劳动的时间不宜过长。","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9c35f5b476","type":"paragraph","text":"以上五条，作为对第五号通令的补充规定，望红卫兵同志们参照执行，望广大革命群众监督和配合我们执行。","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0d21ebe1a9","type":"paragraph","text":"纠察队员有权根据以上规定进行工作，有权干涉和制止一切不符合党的政策的行动。","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cfd42d6692","type":"paragraph","text":"按毛泽东思想办事，按党的政策办事，按十六条办事，决不会束缚我们的手脚，限制我们革命，相反，只能使我们的战斗力更强，使我们更善于革命，使无产阶级文化大革命搞得更好，更彻底，这是一切阶级敌人所最害怕的！","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ec047cbaef","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想是无敌的！","index":22,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4c0ebe067a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想万岁！","index":23,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1cb519ff10","type":"paragraph","text":"首都红卫兵纠察队西城指挥部","index":24,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"25ec9024d8","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六六年九月九日","index":25,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"53b1571666","type":"paragraph","text":"（发表于首都红卫兵纠察队西城指挥部：《首都红卫兵纠察队西城指挥部 通令集（1-10）》）","index":26,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"318ae66629","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}